'''Absolute zero''' was the lowest temperature that could exist and was the point at which all molecular motion stopped.

[[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] used temperatures very close to absolute zero aboard the [[Millennium Falcon/Legends|''Millennium Falcon'']] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]] to [[Death/Legends|kill]] [[voxyn]] captured on his ship.

